        "Episode of Series \"Introducing Chemistry\". Introduces chemical bonding by explaining the different ways in which atoms combine. Illustrates covalent bonds by showing models of hydrogen atoms, their shell structure and methods of bonding. Employs water molecules as examples of polar covalent bonds and sodium chloride molecules as examples of ionic bonds."
